                                                                  EXHIBIT 10.3


                               [WACKENHUT LOGO]

                           THE WACKENHUT CORPORATION

                           EXECUTIVE RETIREMENT PLAN


                           (EFFECTIVE MARCH 1, 1989)


                    As Amended and Revised December 27, 1989
               and As Further Amended and Revised April 24, 1993


