MORTGAGEE HAS IN NO WAY AGREED WITH OR REPRESENTED TO THE PARTIES THAT THE
PROVISIONS OF THIS PARAGRAPH WILL NOT BE FULLY ENFORCED IN ALL INSTANCES.


